snippet.title: Kandria - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Kandria will release on January 11 2023, on Steam, Itch, and as direct download on our website.
Wishlist the game to get notified on launch: https://kandria.com/steam
Join the discussion on Discord: https://kandria.com/discord
